{"tid":435237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅哲斯宣佈設倡導組織 關注一國兩制受損籲英國為香港發聲","createTime":"2017-10-14T05:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T07:51:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"25ad8833c49a49b5a8705f255a9fd2a25764b6bd","tid":435237,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171014/large/1507957707_6a82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171014%2Flarge%2F1507957707_6a82.png&h=3310b64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被港府拒絕入境的英國保守黨人權事務委員會副主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）在網上宣佈，短期內將在英國成立一個倡導組織，關注一國兩制在香港的落實情況。曾在香港生活過5年的羅哲斯稱，自己日前被港府拒絕入境是香港一國兩制正被嚴重侵蝕和受到威脅的活生生例子，認為英國有責任為香港發聲。<br />\n<br />\n由居英港人成立的關注組織「Democracy for Hong Kong」（D4HK）今早透過facebook發佈一段羅哲斯的自拍短片，他呼籲在英國生活的香港人亦和他一起捍衛港人繼續享有人權、自由、民主和法治，他將成立一個倡導組織，並與D4HK緊密合作，喚起英國社會對香港前程的關注。他解釋，英國有份簽署《中英聯合聲明》，故有責任捍衛港人利益，「I think it's our duty in the United Kingdom where we have freedom, we have the possibilty to speak out, to do so, and I hope that we can do that together.」（我認為這是我們的責任，因在英國我們有自由、有機會發聲，我希望我們能一起去做）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57330593&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57330593%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171014&d=n8YxE2uC97LMwMDFKHBdVnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=65a7bf58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57330593%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171014&h=82adeef3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57330593&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171014</a>"},{"pid":"1c97515c4a024ddc341ea272e396734621c59ee7","tid":435237,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a00fb5386ecef2ac255bd299c9a83955fc88e4","tid":435237,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb7d48ea1531dbadeb0639035eab0ea7f77b7085","tid":435237,"uid":22701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"今次真係感謝黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299ee1e6b2e9f3dda85ea59ebb76970dbeb7c1bf","tid":435237,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:53:58.000Z","msg":"五毛又入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99dba0a14229c44dfb6bd4f73a2dba132baa6c92","tid":435237,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"香港冇人理<br />\n英國佬話知你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d570712f46e4eabe76868fc0e5761922e08ca7a1","tid":435237,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"我好想知香港人所謂ga「底線」可以幾低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7812bdd8b7e666dfe61fb595af62097d366ba4c","tid":435237,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"BNO平左權先"},{"pid":"ce2e2a330c16f1e12a20b83e80514080367a5f96","tid":435237,"uid":95617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BNO平左權先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人都無出聲，自己需要就靠自己爭取la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a83fe25824c05d16d62b5ec60067a47a5a33b1","tid":435237,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港冇人理<br />\n英國佬話知你死<img src=\"/assets/f